#!/bin/bash
# Starts watching clipboard and shows list of items by bemenu
ACTION="$@"
PICKER=bemenu
ARGS='-l 30 -n -b -i --fn "Roboto Mono 10" --hb #ffffff --hf #00000 --nb #000000 --nf #ffffff'

case $ACTION in
	clipman)
        clipman pick -t $PICKER --tool-args="$ARGS"
		;;
    watcher)
        wl-paste -t text --watch clipman store 
        ;;
esac

